<section style="background:var(--color-base, #f2ead4); padding:80px 24px;">
  <div style="max-width:800px; margin:0 auto;">
    <p style="font-family:var(--font-sans); font-size:0.75rem; font-weight:700; letter-spacing:0.15em; text-transform:uppercase; color:#b98229; margin-bottom:1rem;">Local Expertise</p>
    <h2 style="font-family:var(--font-serif); font-size:clamp(1.8rem, 3.5vw, 2.8rem); font-weight:400; font-variation-settings:'opsz' 32; line-height:1.2; color:#191817; margin-bottom:1.75rem;">Established northern living with practical convenience.</h2>
    <p style="font-family:var(--font-sans); font-size:1rem; font-weight:300; line-height:1.8; color:#4a4540; margin-bottom:1.25rem;">
      Stafford Heights sits approximately nine kilometres north of the Brisbane CBD, straddling the corridor between the Gympie Road arterial and Kedron Brook. It is an established family suburb that offers more land and more residential space than Kedron or Chermside at a price point that consistently attracts practical, research-led buyers.
    </p>
<!-- APPRAISAL FORM -->
