<!-- END APPRAISAL FORM -->
    <p style="font-family:var(--font-sans); font-size:1rem; font-weight:300; line-height:1.8; color:#4a4540; margin-bottom:1.25rem;">
      I understand what drives Stafford Heights buyers and what sellers need to know before launching a campaign here. The buyer arriving in Stafford Heights has typically been comparing this suburb against Kedron and McDowall for several months. They are buying value relative to those markets, and the campaign needs to be built around that comparison.
    </p>
    <p style="font-family:var(--font-sans); font-size:1rem; font-weight:300; line-height:1.8; color:#4a4540; margin-bottom:1.25rem;">
      The suburb's key amenity is Westfield Chermside, one of Brisbane's largest shopping destinations, which sits less than three kilometres away via Gympie Road. Kedron Brook Bikeway runs along the suburb's southern edge, giving residents access to a significant green corridor that connects to the broader Kedron Brook pathway network. The housing stock is predominantly post-war homes on generous blocks, with a growing number of renovated properties that are resetting the suburb's price ceiling. Properties with Kedron Brook parkland proximity or large rear gardens consistently attract the strongest competition. Stafford Heights State School serves the local catchment and is a positive factor for families with primary-school-age children.
    </p>
    <div style="display:flex; gap:1.5rem; flex-wrap:wrap;">
      <div style="flex:1; min-width:200px; background:#fff; padding:1.75rem; border-left:3px solid #b98229; border-radius:16px;">
        <p style="font-family:var(--font-serif); font-size:1.1rem; font-weight:400; color:#191817; margin-bottom:0.4rem;">Stafford Heights Specialist</p>
        <p style="font-family:var(--font-sans); font-size:0.85rem; font-weight:300; color:#6b6560;">North Brisbane</p>
      </div>
      <div style="flex:1; min-width:200px; background:#fff; padding:1.75rem; border-left:3px solid #b98229; border-radius:16px;">
        <p style="font-family:var(--font-serif); font-size:1.1rem; font-weight:400; color:#191817; margin-bottom:0.4rem;">Kedron Brook Access</p>
        <p style="font-family:var(--font-sans); font-size:0.85rem; font-weight:300; color:#6b6560;">Strong family buyer demand</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <p style="font-size:0.82rem;color:#78716c;margin-top:2rem;">Also selling in: <a href="/suburbs/stafford" style="color:#b98229;">Stafford</a>, <a href="/suburbs/kedron" style="color:#b98229;">Kedron</a>, <a href="/suburbs/everton-park" style="color:#b98229;">Everton Park</a>.</p>
  </div>
</section>

